headline: Why Regeneron (REGN) Shares Are Falling Today
summary: Shares of biotech company Regeneron (NASDAQ:REGN) fell 4.1% in the afternoon session after the company highlighted challenges, including regulatory approvals and competitive pressures, at a healthcare forum.

headline: 1 Safe-and-Steady Stock on Our Watchlist and 2 We Question
summary: A stock with low volatility can be reassuring, but it doesn’t always mean strong long-term performance. Investors who prioritize stability may miss out on higher-reward opportunities elsewhere.
